flavorText: "Thanks for riding, and be sure not to leaf anything behind! Just some tree humor for you."
name: Log Flume
originalText: Visit — Choose up to four creatures you control. Those creatures jump in a log until end of turn. (Creatures in a log together can't be blocked unless they're all blocked. If a spell or ability you control targets one of them, it targets all of them.)
